{"tid":1403693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8月5 全港大三罷 合法勝利條件","createTime":"2019-08-03T20:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T21:25:54.000Z","uid":267471,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a83fc03e950805769bdc49b31b7757f00d27fffa","tid":1403693,"uid":267471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:55:32.000Z","msg":"知道公共交通司機冇可能真係罷到<br />\n但唯一能夠默默有辦法咁支持 就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全港巴士司機 按章工作</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可能唔知 其實本時巴士係為左送客快啲<br />\n埋站出站都冇跟足指引 <br />\n一但巴士可以按章工作 全港交通 必定會<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大停擺</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而其他地鐵 小巴 希望你地都嚴格跟足交通規則或指引 務求能夠真正三罷成功<br />\n<br />\n求下所有司機 加入呢場屬於香港人既戰役<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 加油 🇭🇰</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22b12820276e3dbabf1c420ba392829b7277cee","tid":1403693,"uid":267471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:55:46.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"0366273bb7997d3519022724af9322c06c16d136","tid":1403693,"uid":267471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:55:58.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"4264324d0b4ebd7716cea72c431cdc089722195d","tid":1403693,"uid":267471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:56:08.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"b1bf8da4059f78ac7ebadf739fe3fc1cdb37ea33","tid":1403693,"uid":267471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB